==Demographics==
In the 2020 Decennial Census a population of 473 was determined, 27 of which are Hispanic or Latino. In the 2023 American Community Survey, a Median Household Income was estimated to be $60,938 for a total of 192 households. Regarding education, 19,4% have Bachelor's degrees or higher, and employment is 55,3%.{{US Census population
